	<img height="200" width="300" src="/assets/day-out-at-munroe/14.jpg" />
</div>

<p>We walked along the backwaters and by this time we are already hungry. We decided to eat the authentic Kerala fish food and selected a place according to the local‚Äôs opinion. We went to Ambu Lal‚Äôs Hotel. We were stuck on the other side of the backwater, he then came and took us to his place in his boat.</p>

<div class="gallery" data-rows="3">
	<img height="200" width="300" src="/assets/day-out-at-munroe/15.jpg" />
